Rc8 16. f4 c4 17. Kh1 Ne6 18. Qf3 Ba8 {Gregor,J (2296)-Vokoun,J (2201) Prague
2012 1-0 (85)}) 4... Bb7 5. e4 $146 (5. Rb1 Be7 6. e3 h6 7. Bh4 d6 8. f3 c5 9.
