T (2160)-Neidhardt,C (2420) Germany 2000 0-1 (38)}) 7... Nbd7 8. Nxg6 hxg6 {
White has the pair of bishops} 9. Bg5 (9. h3 Bb4 $11) 9... Be7 (9... Qb6 10.
Rb1 $11) 10. Qe2 Qa5 11. O-O e5 12. dxe5 Nxe5 13. f4 Nxd3 14. Qxd3 O-O-O 15. h3
{Covers g4} (15. a3 Rde8 16. b4 Qb6 $15) 15... Rh5 (15... d4 $5 16. exd4 Rxd4
$17) 16. Rf3 Rdh8 17. Kf2 (17. a3 Re8 $11) 17... Bb4 (17... Qb4 18. Bxf6 Bxf6
19. Rb1 $15) 18. Bxf6 $11 gxf6 {Black has a new doubled pawn: f7} 19. Qd4 f5
20. Ne2 R5h7 21. Qf6 {Black king safety dropped} (21. a3 Be7 $11) 21... Qc7 (
21... Re8 22. c3 Be7 23. Qd4 $15) 22. Qd4 {White threatens to win material:
Qd4xb4. White forks: a7+b4} Qa5 23. Qf6 {Twofold repetition} Bf8 24. c3 {
Consolidates b4} Qc7 25. Qd4 {White threatens to win material: Qd4xa7} Kb8 26.
Qd2 Bg7 27. Rc1 Rd8 28. Rc2 Rhh8 29. Qd1 Rhe8 30. Rd2 Kc8 31. Rg3 Bf6 32. Rf3
Qb6 33. Rd3 $2 (33. b4 $142 $5 $15 {and White has air to breath}) 33... Qxb2
$19 34. Rd2 Qb6 35. Qc1 Re4 36. Rb2 Qc5 37. Qb1 (37. Qd2 Rde8 38. Nd4 Bd8 $19)
37... b6 (37... Rde8 38. Rxb7 Rxe3 39. Rb8+ Kc7 40. Rxe8 Rxe8+ 41. Kf1 $19) 38.
Nd4 Rde8 39. Rc2 Kc7 40. Qb4 $2 (40. Qd1 $142 $19) 40... Bxd4 41. exd4 Qxb4 42.
cxb4 Rxd4 43. b5 (43. a3 {doesn't change the outcome of the game} Rd1 $19)
43... c5 44. Kg1 (44. Ra3 {is the last straw} Kb7 45. g3 $19) 44... Rd1+ 45.
Kh2 d4 46. Rff2 (46. Ra3 {cannot undo what has already been done} Kb8 47. Rc4
Re2 $19) 46... Kd6 47. Kg3 (47. Rc4 {is not the saving move} d3 48. Ra4 Re7 $19
) 47... Kd5 48. Kh4 (48. Rb2 {cannot change destiny} d3 49. Rb3 c4 $19) 48...
f6 (48... f6 49. Rfe2 Rxe2 50. Rxe2 c4 $19) 0-1

