22. a3 {Covers b4} Rc8 23. Bc5 {[%cal Rc5d6,Rd5d6,Gd7d6,Ge6d6] Exerts pressure
on the backward pawn} Rcd8 24. Bb6 {White threatens to win material: Bb6xd8}
Rc8 {Twofold repetition} 25. Be3 Ne7 26. R5d3 Rc6 27. f4 exf4 28. Bxf4 g5 {
Black threatens to win material: g5xf4} 29. Bg3 Ng6 30. Rd5 {Menacing} f6 {
Secures e5} 31. Kf2 Ne5 32. Bxe5 fxe5 {A double rook endgame occured.} 33. Ke3
