{[%mdl 8192] A01: Nimzowitsch-Larsen Opening} 1. b3 e5 2. Bb2 d6 3. e4 Nf6 4.
Nc3 Be7 (4... Nc6 5. Bb5 Bg4 6. Nge2 Be7 7. h3 Bh5 8. O-O O-O 9. Bxc6 bxc6 10.
